WEBVTT

00:13:26.398 --> 00:13:30.140
he says that Mabel
put her hand over her mouth,

00:13:31.417 --> 00:13:33.986
she reached down
and she gave little Fred a hug,

00:13:35.002 --> 00:13:37.579
and then she reached into the icebox,

00:13:37.603 --> 00:13:39.879
and took out a couple Pepsis,

00:13:39.903 --> 00:13:41.359
gave him some Pepsis

00:13:41.383 --> 00:13:44.228
and sent him on his way
to play with his siblings.

00:13:44.948 --> 00:13:46.511
And he said,

00:13:46.535 --> 00:13:52.169
"This was proof that even in the most
harrowing times of race struggle

00:13:52.193 --> 00:13:55.445
that two people could come together
across racial lines

00:13:55.469 --> 00:13:57.665
and find human commonality

00:13:57.689 --> 00:14:00.359
along the lines of love and affection."